  "detailed_description": "New Dork City is in danger! A dangerous alien overlord arrived and is threatening to enslave all humanity! Only a very powerful hero will be able to save us! Are you ready?<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHowever, the only way to increase your power is to search other Heroines and have fun with them! Meet as many as you can and save the city!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nA sexy parody of superhero comics and movies, where you must search multiple Heroines to stop a powerful evil villain.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures<br />\r\n<br />\r\n5 different sexy Heroines.<br />\r\n5 different endings.<br />\r\nErotic comedy.<br />\r\nUnique comic book inspired artwork.<br />\r\nFunny superhero parody.<br />\r\nGameplay<br />\r\n<br />\r\nDifferent endings based on your choices.<br />\r\nNon linear story.",
